Package: SamplerPoisson
Title: Fitting Bayesian Poisson models through different versions of auximialy mixture sampling schemes
Version: 0.0.2
Description: The package allows to fit latent Gaussian models under Poisson likelihood, along with the basic Poisson regression, through the basic improved auxiliary mixture sampling scheme described in Fr√ºhwirth-Schnatter et al. (2009) <doi:10.1007/s11222-008-9109-4> and its robust version introduced in Gardini et. al (2025) <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2502.04938>.
